page.title: 16EXETER AIRPORT:ITS EFFECTS
page.content: {Exeter Airport }is good for my family because we own a pub.People stop in for meals snacks and drinks before a flight.It is good for teenagers because they can get jobs in the cafe. When I am at home a lot of planes go over .Sometimes they are high so they are not very noisy.But if they are low they are very noisy.The big planes are more noisy so I like the little planes best.I think that the planes should not go over at night because it wakes me up.I like the airport because every year there is an air display.
